com.camerontec.catalys.core.session

Class ConnectionPointMatchingUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.core.session.ConnectionPointMatchingUtils

  • public final class ConnectionPointMatchingUtils
extends Object
    Utility methods to help with parties with periods within the components of the each Party. The file string representation of ConnectionPoint is in the form : counterPartyCompID.[counterPartySubID].[counterPartyLocID]~ourCompID.[ourSubID].[ourLocID] If any of the compIDs have period in them then we fail to parse the config correctly. This class contains helper methods to find session references for a given connectionPoint in file string representation.
